tags.name: Edward J. Clark Square
tags.note: Edward J. Clark Square may be at exact intersection with London Street to the southwest. Was designated before intersection realignment.

Cyclists are indeed subject to the lights, though there is no actual reason for requiring this as both the entry and exit are dedicated cycleways with segregation, and there is no pedestrian crossing.
